    <fr:title text="Sober spaces">Sober spaces</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  A topological space <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is <html:em>sober</html:em> if every <fr:link href="/topl-0001/" title="Irreducible space" uri="https://www.my-great-forest.net/topl-0001/" display-uri="topl-0001" type="local">irreducible</fr:link> closed subset is the closure of a <html:em>unique</html:em> point.
</html:p>
